column5: There’s nothing to love and If I do that I will fail which is good.
You need to weaken your immune system to have a higher chance by dying from it and if you do die from it you will probably suffocate to death which is terrible
I think you’ll just suffocate to death which is a pretty bad way to go

Fuck good vibes and I’m not about to hang in this shitty planet much longer
Can’t act happy either because there’s nothing for me to be happy about except for my shows but I’m not happy with that I’m just pleased.

Yup same thing happened to my grandfather when he died from cancer last month. He was fucked up in many different ways with a feeding tube, involuntary bowl movements, loss of hearing, no voice, and a trach that he coughed tons of mucus out of it every minute. There was about 6 times more people at his funeral than the people who saw him actually alive in that disturbing state. During the funeral no fucking human even really cared except for 5 people. If you didn’t see him alive might as well not see him dead. After the funeral some of us got together at a shitty church just to eat and laugh. No one even mentioned him and everyone seemed to forget. There goes the “you’re still not valid part”.

Except for my problem that I am unhelpable with severe deteriorating dark and almost crippling depression and hates everything and everyone. It’s not really even a problem for me because I like having depression because it gets me to suicide and a different perspective but it may be a problem for you.
Me
Yes of course. You’re harming your body by starvation.
Damn why does that happen?
Imagine it

This is pretty dark I imagine slitting both of my wrist in my room and laughing as my arms bleed out in the barrel of water. After that I reach for the p229 Sig Sauer with hollow point bullets and aim it at the upper part of my nose obliterating the most vital parts of my brain. Now after that happens I imagine myself knocking the bloody water barrel all over my hardwood floor while my body has a few muscle contractions and then stops moving completely with brain matter and fluid leaking from my head.
It did not get better for me and it will not because I hate everything and everyone.
Doubt it and if you do the pain would be otherworldly probably.
